<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; background:inherit; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;">To Kill a Mockingbird <span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=To+Kill+a+Mockingbird&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BHarper+Lee%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=July+11%2C+1960&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BJ.+B.+Lippincott+%26+Co.%5D%5D&amp;rft.pages=296+%28first+edition%2C+hardback%29">&#160;</span></td>
